      <description>&lt;h2 id=who-am-i&gt;Who am I?&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;I'm sure I'll talk more about myself as I write here, but I'm a software engineer based in the US.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=why-am-i-making-a-blog&gt;Why am I making a blog?&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;I've recently been reading a &lt;a href='https://ludic.mataroa.blog/'&gt;bunch&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href='https://www.cjthex.com/essays/'&gt;of&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href='https://taalumot.space/essential'&gt;good&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href='https://nonlinear.garden/'&gt;writing&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href='https://www.wheresyoured.at/'&gt;online&lt;/a&gt;, and have felt inspired. I am also a big fan of video essays, and would love to try my hand at that as well someday, but a blog seems like a much more manageable scale, if I'm actually trying to finish anything (which if you're reading this, I have finished at least one blog post. Yay!)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;I sometimes have thoughts that swirl around my head, which won't settle into a coherent shape until I work with them a bit, putting them onto a page. I hope for this to be a space to explore things like that (whatever topics that ends up being over time)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id=what-should-you-expect-here&gt;What should you expect here?&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;I dunno, I'm just as new to this blog as you are!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The current things I'm considering writing about are:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;my yearly theme for 2025: "Year of Weigh Anchor"&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;my requirements/wants for a software engineering job&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;my overall thoughts on the state of tech&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;my thoughts on the quote "We can never see past the choices we don't understand" from The Matrix Reloaded&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;the stock market is bad, and here's why&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We'll see what happens!&lt;/p&gt;
